🎁🌟 HOLIDAY GIVEAWAY 🌟🎁 This holiday season, we're celebrating the moments that matter and the ones that happen when you least expect them. Join us for a special Christmas story, featuring footage shot on the Insta360 X5.

From all of us at Insta360, we wish you a holiday season filled with warmth, fun, and new memories! 🎁 ❤️

Learn more about how we created this holiday story by taking a look behind the scenes in our exclusive interview with director Don Broida. See it here 👉 https://www.insta360.com/blog/creator-stories/capture-what-comes-next-insta360-christmas-2025.html
